{"tid":2324570,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普及彭斯等主要官員　據報最快今日起接種新冠疫苗","createTime":"2020-12-14T04:47:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T05:17:35.000Z","uid":241764,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"94641e75c87cdd3fae2562b6fa72b55e793b7484","tid":2324570,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T04:47:34.000Z","msg":"路透社引述消息報道，美國總統特朗普、副總統彭斯及其他高層官員，最快將於當地星期一起，陸續接種新型冠狀病毒疫苗，作為確保疫情期間政府持續運作計劃的一部分。<br />\n<br />\n全文:<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1565132-20201214.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1565132-20201214.htm&d=WHMLQMiyWmfm849WKe725M2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=ede44058\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1565132-20201214.htm&h=7e68abd1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1565132-20201214.htm</a>"},{"pid":"c9cc659550a501f28ff17ac76441001d82a59dd3","tid":2324570,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T04:54:27.000Z","msg":"習近平幾時接種呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.localpresshk.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/ve.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F03%2Fve.jpg&h=cdf04eea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"35da3b8a1193604a84ad6095b310f9e6194f938f","tid":2324570,"uid":147317,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T04:56:30.000Z","msg":"fake new <br />\n<br />\nTrump : <br />\nPeople working in the White House should receive the vaccine somewhat later in the program, unless specifically necessary. I have asked that this adjustment be made. I am not scheduled to take the vaccine, but look forward to doing so at the appropriate time. Thank you!"},{"pid":"579d887f5e55110e64fa1fffacbfea4ad389f3a0","tid":2324570,"uid":263